					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">tokumaru wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">I'm pretty sure that Game Genie codes modify ROM, not RAM.</div><br /><br />The game genie always inserts a 1 into bit 15 of the address ($8000). Not only can it only modify ROM, but it can't modify things in the 6000-7fff range, which can be mapped to ROM.</div>

					
